The paper introduces a new framework for organizing and analyzing high dimensional datasets, which involves mathematical and algorithmic generalization of vector diffusion maps (VDM) and other non-linear dimensionality reduction methods. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
